    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Delicate engravings of spiders and cleomes decorate the silver cover of this magnifying loupe. *White Cleome\u2019s Eye* functions as *spectacles of inquiry*, but the item bonuses granted to Perception checks increase by 1 (so +3 while worn, and +4 to Sense Motive when you activate the artifact).  \n  \nOnce restored, *White Cleome\u2019s Eye* gains the following additional activations.",
